Imposter.description: Tera Steel makes Ditto immune to Toxic Spikes and take less from Stealth Rock. It also lets Ditto revenge kill Belly Drum Hariyama. A Quiet nature and the Special Attack investment is in case Ditto transforms into a Future Sight user like Slowbro.

Physically Defensive.description: 96 Speed EVs lets it outrun max Speed Adamant Bisharp.

Fast Pivot.description: 184 Speed EVs with Jolly Nature lets it outrun max Speed Jolly Gyarados and Slither Wing.

Physically Defensive.description: 64 Speed EVs are to outspeed Adamant Tyranitar.
